<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>お取引の評価 | 慶應教科書フリマ</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        keio: {
                            blue: '#002F6C',
                            red: '#9E0B0E',
                            gold: '#C5A059',
                            dark: '#0B132B'
                        }
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Noto Sans JP', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['Noto Serif JP', 'serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        .keio-stripe {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #002F6C 42%, #9E0B0E 42%, #9E0B0E 58%, #002F6C 58%);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-between">

    <!-- Top Tricolor Pennant Stripe -->
    <div class="keio-stripe h-1.5 w-full sticky top-0 z-50"></div>

    <!-- Navigation Header -->
    <header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-100 shadow-sm sticky top-1.5 z-40">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 group">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-keio-blue to-keio-red rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-md transition-transform group-hover:scale-105">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path d="M4 20L10 14M20 4L14 10" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                        <path d="M10 14L13 11L11 9L8 12L7 15L10 14Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
                        <path d="M14 10L11 13L13 15L16 12L17 9L14 10Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.3"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="font-serif font-extrabold text-base sm:text-lg text-keio-blue leading-tight tracking-wider">
                        慶應教科書フリマ
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest -mt-0.5">
                        Keio Book Loop
                    </p>
                </div>
            </a>
            
            <button onclick="javascript:history.back()" class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-keio-blue flex items-center gap-1 bg-slate-100 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                ← 戻る
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <main class="flex-grow max-w-xl w-full mx-auto px-4 py-10">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden relative">
            <div class="keio-stripe h-1 w-full absolute top-0 left-0"></div>

            <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 border-b border-slate-100 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
                <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 bg-keio-blue/10 text-keio-blue text-[10px] font-bold rounded-md mb-2">
                    取引完了フィードバック
                </span>
                <h2 class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 leading-snug">
                    <%= listing.book.title %> の評価
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">お取引お疲れ様でした。塾生同士の安全でクリーンなコミュニティ維持のため評価をご入力ください。</p>
            </div>

            <form action="/review" method="post" class="p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
                
                <input 
                    type="hidden"
                    name="listingId"
                    value="<%= listing.id %>"
                >

                <!-- Rating Selection -->
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-extrabold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                        取引満足度（星数）
                    </label>
                    <select 
                        name="rating"
                        class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keio-blue focus:bg-white transition-all text-amber-500 font-bold text-base"
                    >
                        <option value="5">★★★★★ （大変満足）</option>
                        <option value="4">★★★★☆ （満足）</option>
                        <option value="3">★★★☆☆ （普通）</option>
                        <option value="2">★★☆☆☆ （やや不満）</option>
                        <option value="1">★☆☆☆☆ （不満）</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <!-- Comment Input -->
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-extrabold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">
                        お取引コメント
                    </label>
                    <textarea
                        name="comment"
                        placeholder="手渡し時のご対応への感謝やコメントなどを記入してください（例：丁寧に対応していただきありがとうございました！）"
                        rows="4"
                        class="w-full p-4 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-keio-blue focus:bg-white transition-all text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-800 placeholder-slate-400 font-medium"
                    ></textarea>
                </div>

                <!-- Submit Buttons -->
                <div class="pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
                    <button 
                        type="submit"
                        class="w-full bg-keio-blue hover:bg-slate-900 text-white font-bold py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg transition-all text-sm tracking-widest text-center"
                    >
                        評価を送信する
                    </button>
                    <button 
                        type="button"
                        onclick="javascript:history.back()"
                        class="w-full sm:w-1/3 text-center bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold py-3.5 px-4 rounded-xl transition-all text-sm tracking-wide"
                    >
                        キャンセル
                    </button>
                </div>

            </form>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 py-6 text-center text-slate-400 text-[10px] tracking-wider">
        &copy; 2026 慶應教科書フリマ (Keio Book Loop) . All Rights Reserved.<br>
        <span class="text-[9px] mt-1 inline-block text-slate-300">「実学の精神」に基づき、塾生同士の知の循環をサポートします。</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>